#Name: RC2FM__Subscript__Show_Custom_Dialog ( param ) History: Created by Automation USA - Julio Toledo Created: 5-31-2017 Last Modified: 6-1-2017 (added commenting) Purpose: Utility subscript used to diplay fully dynamic and customizable alerts Parameters: Script Parameter string for the alert message. Other optional parameters include: $$Title (defaults to "Alert") $$DefaultButton (defaults to "OK") $$Button2 (defaults to null) $$Button3 (defaults to null) Important Notes: None
If [ not IsEmpty ( Get (ScriptParameter ) ) ]
If [ Abs ( Get ( SystemPlatform ) ) = 3 //Platform mobile ]
If [ IsEmpty ( $$Button2 ) and IsEmpty ( $$Button3 ) ]
Show Custom Dialog [ Title: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Title ) ; "Alert" ; $$Title ); Message: Get ( ScriptParameter ), Default Button: If ( IsEmpty ( $$DefaultButton ) ; "OK" ; $$DefaultButton ), Commit: “No” ]
Else If [ IsEmpty ( $$Button3 ) and not IsEmpty ( $$Button2 ) ]
Show Custom Dialog [ Title: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Title ) ; "Alert" ; $$Title ); Message: Get ( ScriptParameter ), Default Button: If ( IsEmpty ( $$DefaultButton ) ; "OK" ; $$DefaultButton ), Commit: “No”, Button 2: $$Button2, Commit: “No” ]
Else If [ IsEmpty ( $$Button2 ) and not IsEmpty ( $$Button3 ) ]
Show Custom Dialog [ Title: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Title ) ; "Alert" ; $$Title ); Message: Get ( ScriptParameter ), Default Button: If ( IsEmpty ( $$DefaultButton ) ; "OK" ; $$DefaultButton ), Commit: “No”, Button 2: $$Button3, Commit: “No” ]
Else
Show Custom Dialog [ Title: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Title ) ; "Alert" ; $$Title ); Message: Get ( ScriptParameter ), Default Button: If ( IsEmpty ( $$DefaultButton ) ; "OK" ; $$DefaultButton ), Commit: “No”, Button 2: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Button2 ) ; "" ; $$Button2 ), Commit: “No”, Button 3: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Button3 ) ; "" ; $$Button3 ), Commit: “No” ]
End If
Else
Show Custom Dialog [ Title: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Title ) ; "Alert" ; $$Title ); Message: Get ( ScriptParameter ), Default Button: If ( IsEmpty ( $$DefaultButton ) ; "OK" ; $$DefaultButton ), Commit: “No”, Button 2: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Button2 ) ; "" ; $$Button2 ), Commit: “No”, Button 3: If ( IsEmpty ( $$Button3 ) ; "" ; $$Button3 ), Commit: “No” ]
End If
Set Variable [ $$Title; Value:"" ]
Set Variable [ $$DefaultButton; Value:"" ]
Set Variable [ $$Button2; Value:"" ]
Set Variable [ $$Button3; Value:"" ]
Go to Field [ ] [ Select/perform ]
Else
Exit Script [ Result: 958 ]
End If
